{"tid":1710111,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"西灣河中槍義士仍危殆須再接受手術　被燒傷馬鞍山廢老3成皮膚燒傷","createTime":"2019-11-12T05:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T05:51:47.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"780d7eb7cf1b66c851d11f3f975d20334c939a0b","tid":1710111,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1491552_1_L_20191112113411.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1491552_1_L_20191112113411.jpg&h=37073755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨日西灣河衝突中中槍受傷的21歲男子，目前情況仍然危殆，消息指，佢腹部中槍，要接受肝臟和腎臟手術，現時仍在東區醫院深切治療部留醫。<br />\n<br />\n至於昨天在馬鞍山懷疑被人淋易燃液體後點火燒傷的57歲男子，據了解他有3成皮膚二級燒傷，目前仍在沙田威爾斯醫院深切治療部留醫。<br />\n<br />\n昨日多區發生衝突，共128人受傷送院，除兩名危殆男子外，另外4人情況嚴重，63人情況穩定，58人已出院，尚有1人暫時未確定情況。"},{"pid":"0b9c2ecfe77893739e4e0b8fbf7fa1987de1a747","tid":1710111,"uid":214534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:44:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">得3成都話危殆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"5d0bc8fada115cbe1b4fe9a6e775efba4dc93c97","tid":1710111,"uid":283189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:44:51.000Z","msg":"唔洗驚，十成都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87580862b09d355f1156b82f9c6b0b4cb8aad8fc","tid":1710111,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:44:57.000Z","msg":"特技人<br />\n收左錢<br />\n自編自導<br />\n俾人利用左"},{"pid":"29e9b3b5645dddd92914d72fcf60dfb550231a89","tid":1710111,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:45:22.000Z","msg":"收左錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8219cecf1a77d31a41f9401876060c5d4a545522","tid":1710111,"uid":194130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu